    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for anyone looking for dependable transportation at an affordable price point. Mechanically, the engine starts up without issue and the transmission shifts through all gears, though you should expect the typical driving feel of an older vehicle. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some minor dings, and paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the cabin is functional but exhibits significant wear on the upholstery and some staining on the carpets. While it isn't a showpiece, it has been regularly serviced and is ready to be driven daily.",
