    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been so reliable and still drives like a dream! It\u2019s in really solid shape, well-loved, and totally ready for all your upcoming road trips. Whether you're commuting or heading out for a weekend getaway, this car is super comfortable and a total joy to drive. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re really going to love it!",
