      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46-generation BMW M3 is a mechanically sound example of the marque\u2019s high-revving zenith. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for exceptional throttle response. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a Getrag six-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock. The chassis maintains its structural integrity with documented subframe reinforcement, while the suspension geometry remains true for precise turn-in. Finished in a respectable driver-quality aesthetic, this M3 is a purist\u2019s tool ready for the canyon or the circuit.",
